=head2 InitiationMethod => Str

Indicates how the contact was initiated.


=head2 InitiationTimestamp => Str

The date and time this contact was initiated, in UTC time. For
C<INBOUND>, this is when the contact arrived. For C<OUTBOUND>, this is
when the agent began dialing. For C<CALLBACK>, this is when the
callback contact was created. For C<TRANSFER> and C<QUEUE_TRANSFER>,
this is when the transfer was initiated. For C<API>, this is when the
request arrived. For C<EXTERNAL_OUTBOUND>, this is when the agent
started dialing the external participant. For C<MONITOR>, this is when
the supervisor started listening to a contact.


